    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! You honestly have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolute pristine condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and making sure every inch stays spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel inside. I'm really looking for a great new home for it, so if you want a ride that's been loved and meticulously maintained, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
