    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that remains in peak operational synchronization. This power is channeled through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, providing unparalleled mechanical feedback. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain the integrity of its sophisticated multi-link rear suspension. The exterior retains its original factory finish with perfect panel alignment and no evidence of thermal cycling fatigue on the cooling system components. This is a turn-key specimen for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and chassis rigidity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
