    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior features original, factory-correct paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the chrome and rubber trim remain supple and vibrant. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are firm and unmarked, completely free of bolster wear or fading. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is meticulously detailed, housing a powertrain that has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy and strictly OEM parts. This vehicle has been garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. Full service documentation is included, verifying a history of rigorous preventative maintenance. This is an investment-quality example for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
